{"tid":1120191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"著住校服扑野真係好正","createTime":"2019-04-22T13:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T13:48:37.000Z","uid":99568,"like":42,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aab0b814efc684f6542cf4decc495679254b3e97","tid":1120191,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左三年 <br />\n扑野方面真係咩花式都玩過哂 <br />\n呢排覺得自己開始無咩想搞佢既衝動 <br />\n<br />\n但就係尋晚 佢突然話想著住校服比我搞 <br />\n<br />\n我: 去邊度買校服呀? <br />\n佢: 著番我中學個套囉 <br />\n<br />\n佢係衣櫃拎左套校服出黎著左上身 <br />\n我即刻好似撻著左咁撲低左佢 <br />\n<br />\n我:一齊三年而家先知你讀慈幼 <br />\n佢: 嘻嘻 傻豬 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁 <br />\n我地就渡過左激情既夜晚 <br />\n詳細唔多講 <br />\n但我覺得我地既關係已經修補左"},{"pid":"d8b27bbcb64ea4d0d18e87d700e66fd9339c4381","tid":1120191,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b148f7e3283219e836bc81caf15f412eadb11","tid":1120191,"uid":35468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"Gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a207ee85645d811959c12fbc7989e23f3dc4472b","tid":1120191,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890d545ac286030d9cfbcc8a30fca0b2209823d0","tid":1120191,"uid":57021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db473c63236dc490d5089cf731f7b69d2177cc0c","tid":1120191,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d5b148f7e3283219e836bc81caf15f412eadb11","tid":1120191,"uid":35468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-2